{
  "page": "Jorah (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mormont\" title=\"Jorah Mormont\">Jorah Mormont</a></b> is an exiled knight in service to House Targaryen.\n</p><p>Other characters named <b>Jorah</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Mallister\" title=\"Jorah Mallister\">Jorah Mallister</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Seagard\" title=\"Lord of Seagard\">Lord of Seagard</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jorah_Stark\" title=\"Jorah Stark\">Jorah Stark</a>, an ancient <a href=\"/index.php/King_in_the_North\" title=\"King in the North\">King in the North</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403205102\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26763-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403205102 and revision id 245363\n -->\n",
